---
title: HelloHero: Spiced Beef Rump & Jewel Couscous with Yoghurt & Almonds
description: Eat the tropical rainbow tonight with this vibrant collection of veggies and beef rump cooked in our mild Caribbean jerk seasoning. We’re keeping those beach vibes going by adding a charred pineapple slaw, coconut sauce and a hint of nutty peanuts.

